OL,3,CDoctors call for extra funding to end
OL,4,Cthe '8am scramble' for appointments
OL,6,FLabour will struggle to meet its
OL,7,Fpledge to "end the 8am scramble" for
OL,8,Fdoctor's appointments without
OL,9,Fincreasing core funding for GPs, a
OL,10,Fdoctors' organisation has warned.
OL,12,FDuring the election campaign, Health
OL,13,FSecretary Wes Streeting said Labour
OL,14,Fwould "end the 8am scramble by
OL,15,Fallowing patients to easily book
OL,16,Fappointments to see the doctor they
OL,17,Fwant, in the manner they choose".
