OL,3,CDoctors call for extra funding to end
OL,4,Cthe '8am scramble' for appointments
OL,6,FBut the Doctors' Association UK said
OL,7,Fmore funding is needed with the
OL,8,Forganisation's GP lead Dr Lizzie
OL,9,FToberty saying at least another #35
OL,10,Fper patient per year is required to
OL,11,Fmatch funding levels from a decade ago.
OL,13,F"We receive (the same) payment per
OL,14,Fpatient, per year, no matter how
OL,15,Fcomplex, no matter what they need
OL,16,Fdoing, no matter how many appointments
OL,17,Fthey have," she told the i newspaper.
