OL,3,CDoctors call for extra funding to end
OL,4,Cthe '8am scramble' for appointments
OL,6,F"(The) payment has not been uplifted
OL,7,Fin line with inflation or patient
OL,8,Fneed, so over the years primary care
OL,9,Fhas had to do more and more with less
OL,10,Fand less, which can be seen in the
OL,11,Fdifficulties people have in getting to
OL,12,Fsee their GP."
OL,14,FWhile GP funding comes through several
OL,15,Fchannels, compensation is also
OL,16,Fdetermined by the number of patients
OL,17,Fregistered to each practice,
OL,18,Fregardless of need.
