OL,6,FRecent figures reported the NHS paid
OL,7,Fan average of #164.64 for each
OL,8,Fregistered patient in 2022/23.
OL,10,FResearch from the King's Fund released
OL,11,Fin May reported 48% of Britons wanted
OL,12,Fto "increase taxes and spend more on
OL,13,Fthe NHS".
OL,15,FMore than five million people waited
OL,16,Fup to a week to be seen by a doctor,
OL,17,Faccording to the latest official
OL,18,Ffigures.
