OL,3,CDoctors call for extra funding to end
OL,4,Cthe '8am scramble' for appointments
OL,6,FIn July, the Health Secretary
OL,7,Fcommissioned a comprehensive report
OL,8,Fled by health minister Lord Ara Darzi
OL,9,Fon the state of the struggling health
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,13,Fspokesperson told the PA news agency:
OL,14,F"The NHS is broken and we want to
OL,15,Fshift the focus out of hospitals and
OL,16,Finto the community, fixing the front
OL,17,Fdoor of the NHS and ending the misery
OL,18,Fof people waiting weeks for a GP
OL,19,Fappointment.
