OL,3,CDoctors call for extra funding to end
OL,4,Cthe '8am scramble' for appointments
OL,6,F"We have committed to recruiting over
OL,7,F1,000 newly qualified GPs through an
OL,8,F#82 million boost to the Additional
OL,9,FRoles Reimbursement Scheme and cutting
OL,10,Fred tape.
OL,12,F"This Government is also accepting the
OL,13,FReview Body on Doctors' and Dentists'
OL,14,FRemuneration's (DDRB) pay
OL,15,Frecommendation of a 6% uplift to pay
OL,16,Fand is consulting on the
OL,17,Fimplementation."
