OL,6,FEarlier this month, the British
OL,7,FMedical Association announced members
OL,8,Fwould take industrial action over a
OL,9,Fnew contract for GP surgeries in
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FIn July, nearly 10,000 doctors signed
OL,13,Fan open letter to Mr Streeting, urging
OL,14,Fthe Government to review the NHS Long
OL,15,FTerm Workforce Plan with a focus on
OL,16,Fstaff retention, training and resource
OL,17,Fmanagement.
